@startuml
title SAGA Checkout - Combined View
hide footbox

participant Client
participant "Order service" as Order
participant Coordinator
participant "Stock service" as Stock
participant "Payment service" as Payment
participant "Recovery worker" as Recovery

legend right
|<#2E8B57>| normal progress |
|<#B22222>| failure branch |
|<#D97706>| recovery or undo |
endlegend

note over Client,Recovery #FFF8DC
Recovery may finish the transaction after the original
client request has already timed out.
end note

Client -[#2E8B57]> Order : Ask to check out the order.

alt The order does not exist
  Order -[#B22222]> Client : Reject the request.
  note over Client,Order #FDEDEC
  End: request rejected.
  end note

else Another checkout already holds the guard
  Order -[#B22222]> Client : Reject the request because checkout is already in progress.
  note over Client,Order #FDEDEC
  End: request rejected.
  end note

else The order is already paid
  Order -[#2E8B57]> Client : Return success immediately.
  note over Client,Order #E8F8F5
  End: already paid success.
  end note

else The order is valid and no other checkout is running
  Order -[#2E8B57]> Order : Validate the order and acquire the checkout guard.
  Order -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : Start the coordinator transaction.

  group HOLD stage
    par Stock HOLD branch
      Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Stock : Try to reserve the items for HOLD.
    else Payment HOLD branch
      Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Payment : Try to reserve the money for HOLD.
    end

    alt Both HOLD replies say ok
      Stock -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : HOLD ok.
      Payment -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : HOLD ok.
      Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Order : Mark the order as paid.

      alt The order write succeeds
        Order -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : The order is now paid.
        Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : Record COMMIT.

        group COMMIT stage
          par Stock COMMIT branch
            Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Stock : Finish COMMIT for the reservation.
          else Payment COMMIT branch
            Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Payment : Finish COMMIT for the money hold.
          end

          alt Both COMMIT confirmations arrive
            Stock -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
            Payment -[#2E8B57]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
            Coordinator -[#2E8B57]> Order : Clear the checkout guard.
            Order -[#2E8B57]> Client : Return success.
            note over Client,Order #E8F8F5
            End: success.
            end note

          else A COMMIT confirmation is missing,\na COMMIT publish fails,\na participant returns an error,\na wrong-phase reply is ignored,\nor the coordinator stops after the order is paid
            Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : The transaction needs recovery after the paid boundary.
            note over Coordinator,Payment #FDEDEC
            This branch covers:
            - stock COMMIT confirmation lost
            - payment COMMIT confirmation lost
            - COMMIT publish failure
            - participant error during COMMIT
            - stale HOLD reply ignored while waiting for COMMIT
            - coordinator crash after the order was paid
              but before the transaction was safely closed
            end note

            Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Inspect the state and move forward.
            Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Because the order is already paid,\nfinish COMMIT instead of undoing work.

            par Finish stock COMMIT
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the reservation.
              Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
            else Finish payment COMMIT
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the money hold.
              Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
            end

            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
            note over Order,Recovery #E8F8F5
            End: success after recovery.
            end note
          end
        end

      else The order write fails,\nor the coordinator stops before the paid boundary is safely resolved
        Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : Start RELEASE and REFUND now.
        note over Coordinator,Recovery #FDEDEC
        This branch covers:
        - the order database write failed
        - coordinator crash after both HOLD replies
          but before the paid boundary was safely resolved
        end note

        group Undo stage
          par Undo stock HOLD
            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : RELEASE the reservation.
          else Undo payment HOLD
            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : REFUND or RELEASE the money hold.
          end

          alt Both undo confirmations arrive
            Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : RELEASE confirmed.
            Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : REFUND or RELEASE confirmed.
            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
            note over Order,Recovery #FCF3CF
            End: checkout aborted.
            end note

          else A RELEASE or REFUND confirmation is missing,\na RELEASE publish fails,\na participant returns an error,\na wrong-phase reply is ignored,\nor the coordinator stops during undo
            Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : The transaction now needs recovery.
            note over Coordinator,Payment #FDEDEC
            This branch covers:
            - stock RELEASE confirmation lost
            - payment REFUND confirmation lost
            - RELEASE or REFUND publish failure
            - participant error during RELEASE or REFUND
            - stale HOLD reply ignored while waiting for RELEASE
            - coordinator crash during undo
            end note

            Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Inspect what already happened.

            alt The order is already paid
              Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Move forward and finish COMMIT.

              par Finish stock COMMIT
                Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the reservation.
                Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
              else Finish payment COMMIT
                Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the money hold.
                Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
              end

              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
              note over Order,Recovery #E8F8F5
              End: success after recovery.
              end note

            else The order is not safely paid
              Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Continue RELEASE and REFUND.

              par Continue stock undo
                Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : RELEASE the reservation.
                Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : RELEASE confirmed.
              else Continue payment undo
                Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : REFUND or RELEASE the money hold.
                Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : REFUND or RELEASE confirmed.
              end

              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
              note over Order,Recovery #FCF3CF
              End: checkout aborted after recovery.
              end note
            end
          end
        end
      end

    else HOLD does not finish cleanly,\nor the coordinator stops during HOLD
      Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : Record ABORT and start RELEASE and REFUND now.
      note over Coordinator,Payment #FDEDEC
      This branch covers:
      - stock reject
      - payment reject
      - timeout or lost reply
      - HOLD publish failure
      - coordinator crash before both HOLD replies
        were safely handled
      end note

      group Undo stage
        par Undo stock HOLD
          Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : RELEASE the reservation.
        else Undo payment HOLD
          Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : REFUND or RELEASE the money hold.
        end

        alt Both undo confirmations arrive
          Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : RELEASE confirmed.
          Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : REFUND or RELEASE confirmed.
          Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
          note over Order,Recovery #FCF3CF
          End: checkout aborted.
          end note

        else A RELEASE or REFUND confirmation is missing,\na RELEASE publish fails,\na participant returns an error,\na wrong-phase reply is ignored,\nor the coordinator stops during undo
          Coordinator -[#B22222]> Coordinator : The transaction now needs recovery.
          note over Coordinator,Payment #FDEDEC
          This branch covers:
          - stock RELEASE confirmation lost
          - payment REFUND confirmation lost
          - RELEASE or REFUND publish failure
          - participant error during RELEASE or REFUND
          - stale HOLD reply ignored while waiting for RELEASE
          - coordinator crash during undo
          end note

          Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Inspect what already happened.

          alt The order is already paid
            Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Move forward and finish COMMIT.

            par Finish stock COMMIT
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the reservation.
              Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
            else Finish payment COMMIT
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : Retry or confirm COMMIT for the money hold.
              Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : COMMIT confirmed.
            end

            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
            note over Order,Recovery #E8F8F5
            End: success after recovery.
            end note

          else The order is not safely paid
            Recovery -[#D97706]> Coordinator : Continue RELEASE and REFUND.

            par Continue stock undo
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Stock : RELEASE the reservation.
              Stock -[#D97706]> Coordinator : RELEASE confirmed.
            else Continue payment undo
              Coordinator -[#D97706]> Payment : REFUND or RELEASE the money hold.
              Payment -[#D97706]> Coordinator : REFUND or RELEASE confirmed.
            end

            Coordinator -[#D97706]> Order : Clear the checkout guard if it is still set.
            note over Order,Recovery #FCF3CF
            End: checkout aborted after recovery.
            end note
          end
        end
      end
    end
  end
end
@enduml
